504
00:38:12,604 --> 00:38:14,902
I don't need the company line
right now, okay?

505
00:38:17,509 --> 00:38:18,976
Okay.

506
00:38:19,778 --> 00:38:22,914
Jesus. Listen to me.

507
00:38:22,914 --> 00:38:26,111
All I see is the dark side of everything.

508
00:38:27,518 --> 00:38:29,154
Poor Ruby.

509
00:38:29,154 --> 00:38:31,321
I kill her joy.

510
00:38:31,321 --> 00:38:34,524
Look at her sad, discouraged face.

511
00:38:34,524 --> 00:38:35,889
I don't know what to say.

512
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:41,824
How about,
"Shit, call in the professionals"?

513
00:38:52,875 --> 00:38:56,243
So I guess this is the Freud part,
where I don't say anything...

514
00:38:56,243 --> 00:38:59,474
...and you don't say anything.
All of a sudden, it's:

515
00:38:59,747 --> 00:39:02,978
"Obviously, you wish to sleep
with your father."

516
00:39:03,951 --> 00:39:07,088
So I'm to take it you don't wish to
sleep with your father?

517
00:39:07,088 --> 00:39:08,487
No.

518
00:39:10,758 --> 00:39:13,818
And I don't wanna talk
about my childhood either.

519
00:39:16,263 --> 00:39:18,230
I don't know why I'm here.

